@startuml sequence_static_asset
!theme plain

title Static Asset Delivery Pipeline

actor Browser
participant "CompressionMiddleware" as Compress
participant "StaticFileMiddleware" as StaticFiles
participant "File System" as FS

Browser -> Compress : GET /css/app.a1b2c3d4.css\nAccept-Encoding: br, gzip

Compress -> StaticFiles : Pass request

StaticFiles -> StaticFiles : Match content-hashed filename\nto physical file

StaticFiles -> StaticFiles : Check Accept-Encoding header\nfor supported compression

alt Brotli supported
    StaticFiles -> FS : Read /wwwroot/css/app.a1b2c3d4.css.br
    FS --> StaticFiles : Pre-compressed Brotli file\n(compressed at build time, level 11)
    StaticFiles --> Compress : 200 OK\n+ Content-Encoding: br\n+ Cache-Control: max-age=31536000, immutable\n+ Content-Type: text/css
else Gzip supported
    StaticFiles -> FS : Read /wwwroot/css/app.a1b2c3d4.css.gz
    FS --> StaticFiles : Pre-compressed Gzip file
    StaticFiles --> Compress : 200 OK\n+ Content-Encoding: gzip\n+ Cache-Control: max-age=31536000, immutable\n+ Content-Type: text/css
else No compression supported
    StaticFiles -> FS : Read /wwwroot/css/app.a1b2c3d4.css
    FS --> StaticFiles : Uncompressed file
    StaticFiles --> Compress : 200 OK\n+ Cache-Control: max-age=31536000, immutable\n+ Content-Type: text/css
end

note over Compress : Skips compression\n(already pre-compressed\nor client doesn't support it)

Compress --> Browser : Response with immutable cache headers

note over Browser : Browser caches for 1 year.\nCache busted only when\nfilename hash changes\non redeployment.

@enduml
